reviews.review_text:
Good show, good recording Above average FOB recording of a good performance. Rich Gastwirt has a nice Schoeps > DAT rig. You gotta love the rowdy New England crowd giving the boys energy. Wicked sick GTRFB....this version will cure a bad mood quickly.

Crown noise during Shakedown, but it mostly dissapears for the rest of the show. I think the dudes screaming into the mics got a clue after a little while.

I attended the event. Lots of heads jumped 10' from the stadium onto the field during Shakedown...like water flowing downhill.
